Type: Package
Package: icews
Title: Get ICEWS Event Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Andreas",
           family = "Beger",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "adbeger@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1883-3169"))
Maintainer: Andreas Beger <adbeger@gmail.com>
Description: Download the ICEWS event data from Dataverse and keep it synced
    with the latest updates. Store the local data using either the raw 
    tab-separated files (.tab), in a SQLite database, or both. 
